{"attribution":"National Center for Immunization and Respiratory Diseases (U.S.). Division of Viral Diseases.","cases":[{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p01-001","input":"实现健康平等是指每个人都有公平公正的机会达到最高健康水平。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p01-001","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p01-002","input":"我们都可以在解决不公正现象和克服健康和医疗障碍方面发挥作用。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p01-002","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p01-003","input":"应对 COVID-19 疫情期间， CDC 始终将其健康平等工作的重点放在 COVID-19 及其他严重后果的高风险人群上。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p01-003","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p01-004","input":"请阅读下文的项目描述，详细了解关于 CDC 与受资助合作伙伴通过合作减少 COVID-19 相关健康差异的信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p01-004","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p01-005","input":"目的：开发一套新型工具，社区可以用来监测和解决污名化和种族主义如何影响 COVID-19 的差异。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p01-005","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p01-006","input":"目标是更有效地应对社区中的 COVID-19 和其他公共卫生危机。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p01-006","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p01-007","input":"支持公共卫生从业人员监测与 COVID-19 相关的污名化对历史上被边缘化、种族化和受严重影响的人群的存在、传播和影响。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p01-007","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p01-008","input":"通过向在受 COVID-19 严重影响社区工作、生活和代表社区的可信赖基本服务人员和一线工作人员（例如，社区卫生工作者、药剂师、助产士和社会工作者）提供工具、技术援助和教育，从而充分利用以社区为基础的工作和组织。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p01-008","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p01-009","input":"与少数族裔媒体开展合作，分享向关注的社区传递信息的最佳做法，同时提供社区意见，以供社区工作考虑和采纳。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p01-009","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p03-001","input":"目的：让参与残障研究和外展的全国大学中心和项目网络加入其中，以 1）促进 COVID-19 疫苗沟通， 2）确认疫苗可获得性障碍，以及 3）增强残障群体对疫苗的信心。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p03-001","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p03-002","input":"项目合作伙伴共享可信的 COVID-19 免疫接种信息、应对错误信息、将信息转化为无障碍格式，并分享成功故事和所吸取的教训。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p03-002","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p03-003","input":"此外，大学合作伙伴参与编制易于阅读且可获得的疫苗材料（信息图、故事板报、图像）并将这些材料通过其本地社区内的媒体宣传活动进行传播。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p03-003","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p03-004","input":"目的：制定和执行全国媒体信息传播活动，以增加 AI/AN 社区中的 COVID-19 免疫而集中。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p03-004","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p04-001","input":"目的：建立（AA 和 NH/PI）社区合作伙伴关系，以提供翻译的 COVID-19 信息，满足社区的独特需求、优势和偏好。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p04-001","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p05-001","input":"目的：评估州、部落、地方和地区公共卫生工作者在 COVID-19 疫情期间的心理健康状况，例如抑郁、焦虑、创伤后应激障碍和自杀倾向。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p05-001","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p05-002","input":"项目团队还研究了引发这些后果的风险和缓解因素，并确定了支持心理健康的组织性资源。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p05-002","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p06-001","input":"目的：支持州卫生部门和其他组织倡导 COVID-19 疫情期间的健康生活和社会联系，同时与地方社区合作改善食品和营养安全、体育活动的安全获取以及降低孤立感和孤独感。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p06-001","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p06-002","input":"目的：通过加强与社区组织 (CBO) 的合作伙伴关系并提高 CBO 应对突发公共卫生事件（包括流行病）的能力，改善员工的应急准备和应对做法。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p06-002","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p07-001","input":"目的：招募成熟且值得信赖的组织，动员处于 COVID-19 疾病和死亡风险较高的非裔美国人和非西班牙裔黑人社区采用和保持 COVID-19 预防措施和社区缓解策略。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p07-001","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p08-001","input":"目的：确保更多艾滋病毒感染者获得四个月的每日药品包。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p08-001","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p08-002","input":"该项目还包括更新治疗指导方针，以指定如何以最佳方式做到多月配药，并培训医疗服务提供者实施该过程。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p08-002","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1/p08-003","input":"目的：在受 COVID-19 影响最严重的社区以及 COVID-19 接触、感染和疾病风险更高的人群（包括受到长期健康差异严重影响的人）中培训和部署 CHW，这些 CHW 将通过解决现有的健康差异问题，帮助建立和加强社区对抗 COVID-19 的灵活性。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://stacks.cdc.gov/view/cdc/116683/cdc_116683_DS1.pdf","source_case_id":"p08-003","split":"document"}}],"converter_output_used":false,"dataset":"blind-v2","id":"cdc-stacks-116683-v1","input_only":true,"license":"U.S. Public Domain","modification_notice":"Extracted complete Simplified Chinese introductory and purpose sentences from the checksum-pinned PDF with pypdf 5.9.0, applied Unicode NFC and conservative PDF-whitespace normalization, removed exact within-source duplicates, and added input-only candidate metadata; complex lists, headings, fragments, third-party links, and converter output were excluded, and no expected text was used.","purpose":"candidate_source_pilot","review_policy":"domain_and_risk_must_be_assigned_from_input_only","source_class":"public_domain","stats":{"by_split":{"document":22},"eligible_pending_review":22,"exclusions":{},"raw_cases":22},"upstream_revision":"CDC Stacks cdc:116683; updated 2022-04-22; main document urn:sha256:53fcf122e5009fecf2f7caa24cacbf7a43f55367a3b69ccdbcd69a90eae870a7","version":1}
